I just did a riff on this recipe and it was great. I melted 2 TBS butter, whisked in 1 teas. dijon mustard and 1/4 teas. grated lemon peel, then stirred it all into about 3/4 pound of steamed broccoli and cauliflower, along with about 1 TBS fresh minced chives. A great way to use up extra CSA vegetables!

