We really enjoyed this. The second time around, I added a 'tech of balsamic vinegar, just for fun ('tech is Texan for 'a touch of') and some red bell pepper for color. I also steamed the veggies until barely al dente so when I reheated them -- very slowly to coat well -- in the butter sauce, they turned out perfect.

